<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 18:09:07 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>对于哈马斯来说，加沙医院悲剧是一次叙事胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-18/ty-article/.highlight/for-hamas-the-gaza-hospital-tragedy-is-a-narrative-victory/0000018b-43c2-d242-abef-53e6960a0000</link><description>越来越多的证据更加有力地证明了以色列关于加沙城阿赫利圣公会医院悲剧如何发生的说法，但损害已经造成。与此同时，加沙人将埋葬他们的死者，他们已成为国际影响力游戏中的棋子</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:47:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-10-18/ty-article/.highlight/for-hamas-the-gaza-hospital-tragedy-is-a-narrative-victory/0000018b-43c2-d242-abef-53e6960a0000</guid></item><item><title>新发现改变了哈薛国王攻击圣经迦特的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/new-discovery-changes-story-of-king-hazaels-attack-on-biblical-gath/0000018b-43ab-de3d-a58f-cbeb50e70000</link><description>迦特的非利士人被认为是黎凡特地区使用美索不达米亚风格的烧砖建筑的异类。但在 Tell es-Safi 烧制砖块的并不是窑炉</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:35:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/new-discovery-changes-story-of-king-hazaels-attack-on-biblical-gath/0000018b-43ab-de3d-a58f-cbeb50e70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登在对以色列进行史无前例的战时访问期间回顾了大屠杀和9月11日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-evokes-holocaust-and-september-11-during-unprecedented-wartime-visit-to-israel/0000018b-4352-d614-abcf-eb7346480000</link><description>美国总统宣称“10 月 7 日是自大屠杀以来对犹太人来说最致命的一天”，并发誓“不会再袖手旁观，什么也不做，今天不会，明天不会，永远不会”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/biden-evokes-holocaust-and-september-11-during-unprecedented-wartime-visit-to-israel/0000018b-4352-d614-abcf-eb7346480000</guid></item><item><title>数万人签署请愿书，要求驱逐被视为亲哈马斯的美国教授</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-sign-petitions-demanding-ousters-of-u-s-professors-seen-as-pro-hamas/0000018b-438b-df22-a5eb-4bfbe9360000</link><description>康奈尔大学、哥伦比亚大学和耶鲁大学的教职人员要求解雇那些将哈马斯对以色列南部的袭击形容为令人振奋和震惊的研究员。耶鲁大学的一位教授说：“巴勒斯坦人完全有权通过武装斗争进行抵抗”</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 17:07:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-sign-petitions-demanding-ousters-of-u-s-professors-seen-as-pro-hamas/0000018b-438b-df22-a5eb-4bfbe9360000</guid></item><item><title>“如果她落入哈马斯手中，我们不知道她将如何在克罗恩病中生存”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-shes-in-the-hands-of-hamas-we-dont-know-how-shell-survive-with-crohns/0000018b-4328-de3d-a58f-cb693a160000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特殊项目 ■ Tamar Gutman 很高兴。在与一种使人衰弱的疾病抗争了几年后，她精神焕发，很高兴能够参加超新星音乐节。她的家人谈论她以及收集信息的尝试</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:55:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-shes-in-the-hands-of-hamas-we-dont-know-how-shell-survive-with-crohns/0000018b-4328-de3d-a58f-cb693a160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府未批准解决巴勒斯坦囚犯过度拥挤问题的临时计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-approves-temporal-prison-overcrowding-for-palestinian-prisoners/0000018b-4333-d242-abef-533795bc0000</link><description>十六名以色列立法者投票赞成这项临时规定，该规定将持续三个月，并使该国的监狱即使在满负荷的情况下也能接纳新囚犯</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 15:42:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/israels-knesset-approves-temporal-prison-overcrowding-for-palestinian-prisoners/0000018b-4333-d242-abef-533795bc0000</guid></it